   "source": [
    "# 云服务器安装"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "1) 建立镜像实例（1 GPU ，共享模式）\n",
    " > pytorch-2.5.1 > cuda12.4 > python3.12  \n",
    "\n",
    "2) 启动实例\n",
    "\n",
    "3）启动终端 Terminal ,安装如下python包\n",
    "pip install --upgrade huggingface_hub\n",
    "pip install llama-index-core\n",
    "pip install llama-index-llms-huggingface llama-index-embeddings-huggingface\n",
    "pip install torch transformers accelerate bitsandbytes sentence-transformers\n",
    "pip install chromadb\n",
    "pip install llama-index\n",
    "\n",
    "4）在终端内，下载模型\n",
    "\n",
    "下载embeddings模型\n",
    "cd /root/nas-private/\n",
    "export HF_ENDPOINT=https://hf-mirror.com\n",
    "hf  download BAAI/bge-small-zh-v1.5 --local-dir ./huggingface_cache/BAAI/bge-small-zh-v1.5\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "下载LLM模型 方式1:\n",
    "hf download Qwen/Qwen1.5-7B-Chat --local-dir ./huggingface_cache/Qwen/Qwen1.5-7B-Chat\n",
    "\n",
    "下载LLM方式2:  https://modelscope.cn/\n",
    "pip install modelscope\n",
    "modelscope download --model 'Qwen/Qwen3-8b' --local_dir '/root/nas-private/huggingface_cache/Qwen/Qwen3-8b'\n",
    "\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 本地机器安装"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "1） 安装 Ollama 并下载模型\n",
    "   https://ollama.com/\n",
    "  下载模型\n",
    "   ollama pull qwen3:8b 或 ollama pull qwen2.5:7b\n",
    "   #ollama pull qllama/bge-small-zh-v1.5 \n",
    "   ollama pull nomic-embed-text \n",
    "    \n",
    "\n",
    "2) 安装python 包\n",
    "pip install torch transformers  sentence-transformers\n",
    "pip install chromadb\n",
    "pip install llama-index\n",
    "pip install llama-index-llms-ollama \n",
    "pip install llama-index-embeddings-ollama"
   ]
  },
